title: New York Real Estate Exam Prep
creator: Upward Mobility

extendedInfo.description: Want to ace your New York real estate salesperson/agent/broker exam?  This mobile app contains 644 questions covering essential vocabulary and state exam specific knowledge. Your satisfaction is important to us and we have a no questions asked refund policy for all our Android apps. We encourage you to try our application out risk free and let us know by e-mailing info@upwardpro.com if there are any issues.This app has 233 questions focused on vocab, 200 on general concepts, and another 211 New York specific questions on subject specific knowledge.
